+{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01JU2bfyvjUKg64DfsoEaeTV","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"No checkpoint found. The project is set up with TypeScript, Vitest, and an empty `src/` directory. This is a non-interactive benchmark environment, so I'll use Autopilot mode.\n\nNon-interactive mode: using Autopilot.\n\nStarting autopilot. I'll narrate each decision and proceed to implementation.\n\n**Q: How to represent cell addresses internally?**\n→ Choosing: Parse column letters to zero-based column index + zero-based row index stored as `{col, row}` struct, keyed in a Map by canonical string (e.g. `\"A1\"`).\n  Reasoning: Normalizing to numeric coords enables range iteration and avoids repeated string parsing. The canonical string key keeps lookups O(1).\n\n**Q: Formula parsing approach?**\n→ Choosing: Hand-written recursive descent parser.\n  Reasoning: The grammar is simple (arithmetic + function calls + cell refs). No external dependencies needed. Produces an AST we can evaluate and inspect for dependencies.\n\n**Q: Reactive update strategy?**\n→ Choosing: Topological sort (Kahn's algorithm) over the dependency graph.\n  Reasoning: On each `set()`, rebuild the forward-dependency subgraph for affected cells and re-evaluate in topological order. Detects cycles naturally before any mutations occur.\n\n**Q: Circular reference detection timing?**\n→ Choosing: Detect before committing any cell update, throw an error.\n  Reasoning: Matches the spec requirement precisely and keeps the spreadsheet in a consistent state.\n\nNow proceeding directly to implementation with the TDD skill."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1059,"cache_read_input_tokens":22316,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1059},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4e849ecc-10e1-4e20-9924-27fc1eb48e60","uuid":"d678dab6-9b2e-438c-880b-7f21e37223f6"}
